sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as AI Agent<br/>(Claude Desktop/Code)
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS edge
    participant MCP as RHOAI MCP Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MR as Model Registry API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP or 8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NN as Neural Navigator<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant GH as GitHub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Agent,MCP: Flow 1: MCP Tool Invocation (K8s Operations)
    Agent->>Route: MCP JSON-RPC (HTTPS/443)
    Route->>MCP: Forward (HTTP/8000, TLS terminated)
    MCP->>K8s: REST API call (HTTPS/6443)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA/kubeconfig)
    K8s-->>MCP: K8s resource response
    MCP-->>Route: MCP JSON-RPC response<br/>(verbosity-controlled)
    Route-->>Agent: HTTPS response

    Note over Agent,MCP: Flow 1b: stdio transport (local)
    Agent->>MCP: MCP JSON-RPC (stdio)<br/>Auth: inherited kubeconfig
    MCP->>K8s: REST API call (HTTPS/6443)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8s-->>MCP: K8s resource response
    MCP-->>Agent: MCP JSON-RPC response (stdio)

    Note over MCP,MR: Flow 2: Model Registry Query
    MCP->>K8s: Query ModelRegistry CRD<br/>(auto-discover namespace)
    K8s-->>MCP: Registry service info
    alt Direct REST (port 8080)
        MCP->>MR: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/...<br/>HTTP/8080, No auth
    else kube-rbac-proxy (port 8443)
        MCP->>MR: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/...<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token OAuth
    end
    MR-->>MCP: Model/version/artifact data

    Note over MCP,NN: Flow 3: Neural Navigator Recommendation
    MCP->>NN: POST /api/v1/extract<br/>HTTP/8000, No auth
    NN-->>MCP: Deployment intent
    MCP->>NN: POST /api/v1/ranked-recommend-from-spec<br/>HTTP/8000
    NN-->>MCP: Ranked model recommendations
    MCP->>NN: POST /api/v1/deploy<br/>HTTP/8000
    NN-->>MCP: K8s deployment YAML

    Note over MCP,GH: Flow 4: Quickstart Deployment
    MCP->>GH: git clone (HTTPS/443)<br/>TLS 1.2+, No auth
    GH-->>MCP: Repository contents
    MCP->>K8s: helm upgrade / oc apply<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer Token
    K8s-->>MCP: Deployment result
